WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 18=

01:46.940 --> 01:48.190
If I throw you off here,

01:48.190 --> 01:49.030
what will happen?

01:50.060 --> 01:50.900
Didn't you say

01:50.900 --> 01:51.830
you liked my skull?

01:52.860 --> 01:53.990
If I fall from here,

01:54.750 --> 01:55.910
my head will be crushed.

01:57.060 --> 01:57.900
So will my skull.

02:02.550 --> 02:03.860
Then you should thank your skull

02:04.340 --> 02:05.190
for saving your life.

02:22.700 --> 02:23.540
Simu,

02:24.420 --> 02:25.350
you've been wonderful.

02:27.270 --> 02:28.110
You were,

02:29.550 --> 02:30.390
and you still are.

02:36.300 --> 02:37.140
Duan Shunxi.

03:07.580 --> 03:08.740
This is my home!

03:09.420 --> 03:10.670
You must not trespass!

03:11.580 --> 03:12.830
This is my home!

03:13.350 --> 03:14.670
You must not trespass!

03:21.140 --> 03:21.980
It's the curfew time.

03:22.900 --> 03:23.830
No trespassing.

03:23.830 --> 03:24.900
Why is a spirit there?

03:24.900 --> 03:25.740
No trespassing!

03:26.140 --> 03:26.980
No trespassing.

03:27.350 --> 03:28.190
No trespassing.

03:33.350 --> 03:34.550
This is my home.

03:35.390 --> 03:36.830
No place for your mischief.

03:37.740 --> 03:38.900
I swear to guard this place

03:39.350 --> 03:40.190
without retreat.

03:40.990 --> 03:41.990
No retreat.

03:42.950 --> 03:43.790
No retreat.

03:50.230 --> 03:51.070
Miss,

03:51.790 --> 03:52.790
why are you here?

03:53.620 --> 03:54.830
Don't you know the enemy's coming?

03:56.740 --> 03:58.670
What's your name, sir?

04:02.620 --> 04:03.550
Don't be scared, Miss.

04:04.550 --> 04:06.180
I'm General Zhuisi.

04:06.830 --> 04:08.140
This man is oddly dressed.

04:08.580 --> 04:09.700
He might be a spy.

04:10.230 --> 04:11.070
Let's be cautious.

04:14.420 --> 04:15.260
Zhuisi?

04:18.300 --> 04:19.150
I, all alone,

04:20.180 --> 04:21.710
am equal to an army!

04:25.150 --> 04:25.990
Your real name.

04:30.620 --> 04:32.590
I'm General Zhuisi!

04:33.350 --> 04:35.380
Zhuisi isn't in the Book of Spirits.

04:37.060 --> 04:38.060
Who on earth are you?

04:41.940 --> 04:43.350
Don't be ridiculous!

04:44.150 --> 04:45.910
I am General Zhuisi.

04:47.820 --> 04:49.150
Before my homeland is secured,

04:50.180 --> 04:51.260
I just won't die.

04:53.060 --> 04:53.990
Where my home is,

04:55.150 --> 04:56.300
where I'll be.

04:57.860 --> 04:59.350
I swear to guard this place

05:00.710 --> 05:01.710
without retreat.

05:02.350 --> 05:03.710
No retreat!

05:03.940 --> 05:04.780
Take this.

05:05.260 --> 05:06.100
Stop shouting.

05:21.150 --> 05:22.380
- I don't need this!
- Simu.

05:23.110 --> 05:24.060
He's different

05:24.380 --> 05:25.220
from other spirits.

05:25.620 --> 05:26.670
I'm a general.

05:28.030 --> 05:29.910
How could I lower myself to their level?

05:30.110 --> 05:31.150
He's delirious,

05:31.820 --> 05:33.860
but he can control himself
without spirit stones.

05:34.910 --> 05:35.820
That's really hard.

05:49.230 --> 05:50.070
The day is breaking.

05:51.710 --> 05:52.590
I'll guard the gate.

06:21.150 --> 06:22.350
I remember who Zhuisi is now.

06:23.940 --> 06:25.230
In an ancient book on warfare,

06:25.550 --> 06:26.420
I read about him.

06:27.670 --> 06:29.030
General Zhuisi of the Zhou State

06:29.910 --> 06:30.750
joined the army at a young age

06:31.380 --> 06:32.500
and rose to fame at Yuanlu.

06:33.260 --> 06:34.100
In Luofeng Village,

06:34.350 --> 06:35.420
he was finally besieged

06:36.230 --> 06:37.070
and lost his army.

06:38.710 --> 06:40.110
Oh, it's him.

06:42.860 --> 06:43.700
You know him?

06:44.110 --> 06:44.950
Why does this spirit

06:45.590 --> 06:47.030
mistake himself for Zhuisi?

06:48.260 --> 06:49.790
He must have experienced that war

06:50.710 --> 06:52.060
and lived with these people.

06:53.500 --> 06:55.180
So a sincere heart
can build a connection

06:56.150 --> 06:57.470
even between mortals and spirits.

07:00.860 --> 07:02.180
He stays here for a thousand years

07:02.180 --> 07:03.380
instead of joining a temple.

07:03.550 --> 07:04.860
Yet he can suppress his desires.

07:06.420 --> 07:07.380
This man...

07:09.420 --> 07:11.670
What a pity he doesn't jump
into the Ascension Pool.

07:16.990 --> 07:17.860
What function does

07:18.350 --> 07:19.350
the Pool actually have?

07:21.420 --> 07:22.710
It dissolves obsessions.

07:23.470 --> 07:24.670
Once he jumps, he'll be freed.

07:28.060 --> 07:29.710
If spirits jump into the Ascension Pool,

07:30.940 --> 07:31.910
will it solve the problem

07:31.910 --> 07:33.060
of excessive spirits?

07:33.790 --> 07:34.630
Yes.

07:35.420 --> 07:36.260
But not entirely.

07:37.500 --> 07:39.180
It won't work unless a spirit willingly

07:39.420 --> 07:40.500
lets go of his obsession.

07:41.740 --> 07:42.670
It's almost impossible

07:43.150 --> 07:44.620
to make a spirit willingly jump

07:45.500 --> 07:46.590
into the Ascension Pool.

07:47.590 --> 07:48.670
Otherwise, this spirit

07:48.670 --> 07:49.940
wouldn't have lingered like that.

07:52.550 --> 07:53.390
But why does he guard

07:55.350 --> 07:56.500
by the Ascension Pool?

08:04.860 --> 08:05.710
Your Lordship,

08:05.710 --> 08:07.170
the spirit lingering
by the Pool for a millennium

08:07.180 --> 08:08.020
offended Her Grace.

08:08.500 --> 08:09.470
He's way too powerful.

08:09.470 --> 08:10.550
We are no match for him.

08:10.860 --> 08:11.700
Losers!

08:12.910 --> 08:13.940
Go there with me now.

08:14.180 --> 08:15.020
Yes.

08:26.380 --> 08:27.820
Anyone who violates the decrees

08:28.420 --> 08:29.550
shall be severely punished.

08:31.110 --> 08:32.470
This is my home!

08:33.430 --> 08:34.380
Enemies

08:34.380 --> 08:35.230
shall not invade!

09:17.190 --> 09:18.860
Give me back my family letter!

09:19.500 --> 09:20.830
Give me back my family letter!

09:21.350 --> 09:23.620
Give it back to me!

09:50.430 --> 09:51.270
My letter.

09:58.140 --> 09:58.980
My letter.

09:59.740 --> 10:00.580
Your Grace.

10:11.380 --> 10:12.220
My letter.

10:12.380 --> 10:13.220
My letter.

10:14.140 --> 10:14.980
My letter.

10:17.190 --> 10:18.740
Tell me your real name

10:19.620 --> 10:20.860
and I'll save you.

10:21.430 --> 10:22.270
What do you say?

10:26.190 --> 10:27.900
I'm General Zhuisi.

10:28.900 --> 10:30.950
I'd rather die before subjugation!

10:36.350 --> 10:37.350
Thank you, Yan.

10:38.230 --> 10:40.260
I'll take care of this.

10:40.900 --> 10:42.350
You're being overly lenient.

10:42.900 --> 10:44.310
This spirit interfered with our work

10:44.590 --> 10:45.470
and offended you.

10:45.780 --> 10:46.830
He deserves to be punished.

10:46.990 --> 10:47.830
It doesn't matter.

10:49.260 --> 10:50.190
You should go back.

10:53.660 --> 10:54.500
Yes.

11:04.500 --> 11:05.340
No trespassing.

11:07.310 --> 11:08.150
No trespassing.

11:10.470 --> 11:11.310
No trespassing.

11:12.540 --> 11:13.380
No trespassing.

11:14.230 --> 11:15.260
He thought holding here...

11:15.260 --> 11:16.100
No trespassing.

11:16.230 --> 11:17.230
Was defending his home.

11:18.070 --> 11:18.910
No trespassing.

11:20.510 --> 11:21.350
No trespassing.

11:21.350 --> 11:22.620
He didn't know his nation was in ruins.

11:23.660 --> 11:24.740
He lost his home long ago.

11:26.190 --> 11:27.030
No trespassing.

11:27.470 --> 11:28.310
No trespassing.

11:28.470 --> 11:29.710
Trapped in the past,

11:30.110 --> 11:31.780
he's just tortured by his obsession.

11:32.900 --> 11:34.190
This is totally meaningless.

11:36.070 --> 11:37.310
Trapped here,

11:39.350 --> 11:40.430
he must be very lonely.

11:44.070 --> 11:44.910
No trespassing.

12:05.070 --> 12:12.250
♪Cross your legs for three years♪

12:12.990 --> 12:16.110
♪Subdue dragon and tiger♪

12:17.740 --> 12:18.660
Si,

12:18.660 --> 12:19.500
the hoe I borrowed

12:19.510 --> 12:20.380
is back in your room.

12:21.430 --> 12:22.860
(My fellow villagers)
Thank you, Si.

12:23.230 --> 12:24.140
Si,

12:24.140 --> 12:25.470
eat before you go home.

12:26.140 --> 12:26.990
I get it.

12:26.990 --> 12:27.860
You're back, Si.

12:28.740 --> 12:29.580
That's right.

12:29.830 --> 12:30.670
It's been a while.

12:31.630 --> 12:32.470
Hey, uncle.

12:32.470 --> 12:33.310
Where are you going?

12:33.310 --> 12:34.860
Hi, Si. I'm going out.

12:35.640 --> 12:36.500
Hi.

12:36.500 --> 12:37.340
Busy, huh?

12:38.310 --> 12:39.150
Si,

12:39.540 --> 12:40.380
come over here.

12:41.230 --> 12:42.780
Uncle, why are you sitting here?

12:43.070 --> 12:44.950
I just dried some rice.

12:45.140 --> 12:45.980
Take some back.

12:46.310 --> 12:47.310
I... I can't take it.

12:47.310 --> 12:48.260
Just take it.

12:49.900 --> 12:51.230
- Si.
- Thank you, uncle.

12:51.230 --> 12:52.430
- Si.
- Come on.

12:52.430 --> 12:53.270
Hi, aunt.

12:53.280 --> 12:54.470
I've made you a garment.

12:55.260 --> 12:56.100
Take it.

12:56.900 --> 12:58.150
- Take it.
- Thank you, aunt.

12:59.020 --> 12:59.900
(My fellow villagers)

13:00.830 --> 13:02.070
(in Luofeng Village,)

13:03.260 --> 13:05.190
(I happened to wander
into the Mortal World.)

13:06.140 --> 13:06.980
(Si.)

13:08.500 --> 13:10.070
(You all treated me like your own son)

13:11.020 --> 13:13.850
(and I took you as my family.)
It's delicious. Taste it, aunt.

13:14.820 --> 13:15.660
I'll just

13:15.660 --> 13:16.900
watch you eat.

13:22.950 --> 13:23.960
- Si.
- You're back.

13:24.620 --> 13:25.990
Si.

13:26.700 --> 13:27.540
What's up?

13:27.540 --> 13:29.500
Help me tie my bracelet.

13:30.020 --> 13:30.860
Show me your hand.

13:32.020 --> 13:32.900
I promise you.

13:33.190 --> 13:34.030
If you behave well,

13:34.380 --> 13:35.590
I'll bring you food tomorrow.

13:35.590 --> 13:36.430
Deal?

13:40.190 --> 13:47.190
♪A lamp in the east lights the west♪

13:48.210 --> 13:55.160
♪No lamp in the west,
but it's still bright♪

13:56.240 --> 14:02.990
♪The lamplight gathers like a hood♪

14:03.320 --> 14:10.320
♪What a pity a lamp can't light itself♪

14:54.900 --> 14:55.740
No.

14:56.590 --> 14:57.430
No.

14:58.310 --> 14:59.150
No.

14:59.380 --> 15:00.220
No!

15:00.500 --> 15:02.020
No!

15:06.310 --> 15:07.150
My family letter.

15:07.780 --> 15:08.620
My letter.

15:10.110 --> 15:11.020
My letter.

15:11.020 --> 15:12.430
Do you remember who you are now?

15:14.140 --> 15:14.980
Si.

15:18.620 --> 15:20.860
(Si)

16:00.590 --> 16:01.430
Granny.

16:03.430 --> 16:04.270
Granny.

16:05.430 --> 16:06.270
Granny.

16:07.990 --> 16:10.190
Granny, what happened?

16:10.190 --> 16:11.540
Granny.

16:13.070 --> 16:14.430
Granny.

16:15.230 --> 16:16.950
Granny!

16:59.190 --> 17:00.030
Si,

17:00.620 --> 17:01.860
you were a spirit wandering

17:02.350 --> 17:03.380
in the Mortal World.

17:04.020 --> 17:05.430
You once lived in Luofeng Village.

17:06.500 --> 17:07.990
Later, the war broke out nearby.

17:08.720 --> 17:10.390
Luofeng Village was in danger.

17:10.990 --> 17:12.580
Zhuisi retreated to this place

17:12.580 --> 17:13.670
and lost his army.

17:14.060 --> 17:15.860
Then you put on his armor

17:16.230 --> 17:17.430
and guarded Luofeng Village.

17:18.670 --> 17:20.020
Later, you returned to the Void

17:20.470 --> 17:21.500
and guarded here.

17:32.230 --> 17:35.990
How did I get my memories back?

17:36.580 --> 17:37.540
Since you remembered,

17:39.470 --> 17:40.740
why did you see yourself as him?

17:47.870 --> 17:49.670
General Zhuisi once said,

17:51.820 --> 17:53.150
"My homeland won't be safe

17:54.020 --> 17:55.430
until the war is over.

17:56.820 --> 17:58.190
My clan is destroyed.

17:58.630 --> 17:59.780
There's no way of reunion."

18:01.670 --> 18:03.470
I refused to believe this grievous news.

18:04.870 --> 18:06.990
So, I pretended to be General Zhuisi

18:08.020 --> 18:09.630
and appointed myself as the gatekeeper,

18:10.630 --> 18:12.060
looking for a way home.

18:15.230 --> 18:16.580
For as long as I can remember,

18:17.710 --> 18:19.430
I've stayed by the Ascension Pool

18:20.150 --> 18:21.470
and guarded it day and night

18:21.780 --> 18:22.950
without leaving.

18:28.190 --> 18:29.390
I want to go home.

18:31.150 --> 18:32.580
You aren't General Zhuisi.

18:33.230 --> 18:34.150
But you tried your best

18:34.150 --> 18:35.150
to protect your homeland.

18:36.500 --> 18:37.780
This battle is over.

18:39.260 --> 18:40.150
It's time to let it go.

18:44.630 --> 18:46.060
But I have no home now.

18:55.060 --> 18:56.230
What is a home?

18:58.990 --> 19:00.820
A house without the warmth of life

19:03.670 --> 19:05.390
or a memory that only you remember?

19:08.190 --> 19:09.870
Your relatives and friends

19:10.300 --> 19:11.140
you've missed...

19:12.870 --> 19:14.260
They have left you.

19:16.780 --> 19:17.990
No one remembers you now.

19:23.430 --> 19:24.270
No.

19:26.300 --> 19:27.140
No.

19:30.580 --> 19:32.150
I don't want to forget them.

19:37.500 --> 19:39.190
I don't want that.

19:40.100 --> 19:43.780
I just don't!

20:55.230 --> 20:56.740
Si, come on.

20:56.750 --> 20:57.600
Aunt.

20:57.600 --> 20:58.910
I've made you a garment.

20:59.060 --> 21:01.260
I'll make you nice food. Wait for me.

21:01.260 --> 21:02.190
If you behave well,

21:02.190 --> 21:03.390
when I come back tomorrow,

21:03.670 --> 21:04.580
I'll bring you food.

21:04.580 --> 21:05.950
Thank you, Si.

21:05.950 --> 21:06.790
Go ahead and play.

21:07.260 --> 21:08.820
If it's delicious, eat some more.

21:08.820 --> 21:09.660
Si,

21:09.890 --> 21:10.740
come over here.

21:10.740 --> 21:11.580
I just

21:11.710 --> 21:12.820
dried some rice.

21:13.020 --> 21:13.860
Take some back.

21:16.870 --> 21:17.740
Si.

21:18.710 --> 21:19.550
Uncle.

21:43.340 --> 21:44.630
He is finally at peace, huh?

21:46.740 --> 21:47.740
He won't remember

21:49.300 --> 21:50.580
the misery of war and separation.

21:59.470 --> 22:00.780
I heard that a spirit

22:00.780 --> 22:01.950
let it go and ascended.

22:02.100 --> 22:03.630
Her Grace sent him personally.

22:04.500 --> 22:06.190
Previously, Her Grace ordered us

22:06.470 --> 22:07.630
to persuade spirits to ascend

22:08.190 --> 22:09.820
and resolve excessive spirits.

22:10.300 --> 22:11.190
Now,

22:11.580 --> 22:12.500
Her Grace has issued

22:12.500 --> 22:13.430
the Ascension Decree.

22:14.150 --> 22:15.820
She wants us
to let go of our obsessions.

22:20.820 --> 22:21.710
If I had known

22:21.710 --> 22:22.870
about the punishment

22:23.500 --> 22:24.430
for not fulfilling that,

22:24.430 --> 22:25.870
I should have worked harder

22:26.100 --> 22:27.260
to make more spirit stones.

22:28.710 --> 22:30.100
If you complain instead of working,

22:30.670 --> 22:32.100
Her Grace might send you to ascend.

22:32.580 --> 22:33.500
With strong obsessions,

22:33.870 --> 22:34.710
I can't ascend.

22:38.990 --> 22:39.830
Hurry up.

22:39.990 --> 22:41.190
We'll finally see off spirits

22:41.190 --> 22:42.100
who have moved on.

22:51.260 --> 22:52.820
We spirits are born from obsessions.

22:53.230 --> 22:54.710
So, there are 24 temples in the Void.

22:54.880 --> 22:55.720
There's a lord

22:55.720 --> 22:56.780
for each temple.

22:57.150 --> 22:58.500
Every spirit coming in here

22:58.500 --> 22:59.780
must choose a temple accordingly.

23:00.150 --> 23:00.990
Different obsessions

23:01.190 --> 23:02.300
take them where they belong.

23:04.300 --> 23:05.300
What types of obsessions?

23:06.260 --> 23:07.470
For example, in Jiling Temple

23:07.630 --> 23:08.910
are mischievous children.

23:09.540 --> 23:10.740
Shaoling Temple values looks.

23:10.910 --> 23:12.150
Zhuangling Temple desires power.

23:12.670 --> 23:13.780
Yan Ke's Qiling Temple

23:13.780 --> 23:14.740
commands the forces.

23:14.910 --> 23:15.990
Jiang Ai's Xuling Temple

23:15.990 --> 23:17.820
governs the biggest pleasure den here.

23:18.230 --> 23:20.820
That's a paradise that combines

23:20.820 --> 23:22.190
wealth, power, wine, and lust.

23:22.430 --> 23:23.270
Especially the casino

23:23.270 --> 23:24.580
she's personally in charge of.

23:26.260 --> 23:29.460
(Xuling Temple, the Void)

23:31.060 --> 23:34.740
(Ledger)

24:16.340 --> 24:17.180
Somebody.

24:18.230 --> 24:19.070
Here.

24:21.300 --> 24:22.140
Our guest is here.

24:22.500 --> 24:23.340
Yes.

24:25.710 --> 24:26.550
Here we are.

24:33.150 --> 24:33.990
This is it?

24:34.630 --> 24:35.470
Let's go.

24:46.190 --> 24:47.060
I bet on big.

24:55.030 --> 24:56.740
Hey, man.

24:56.740 --> 24:57.580
Give me money.

24:57.910 --> 24:58.750
What for?

24:59.020 --> 24:59.870
Otherwise,

24:59.870 --> 25:00.990
we can't even make our way

25:00.990 --> 25:01.830
into this place.

25:07.540 --> 25:09.670
This is all the money I have.

25:11.470 --> 25:12.670
I'm borrowing it.

25:13.430 --> 25:14.740
I'll return every bit of it.

25:24.630 --> 25:29.740
Open it!

25:29.740 --> 25:30.670
I won!

25:33.060 --> 25:33.990
Come on. Let me try.

25:48.910 --> 25:50.230
Come on. One more time.

25:51.100 --> 25:52.390
It's all mine.

26:07.950 --> 26:08.790
I won!

26:08.940 --> 26:09.780
I won!

26:09.780 --> 26:10.620
They're all mine.

26:11.340 --> 26:12.470
My spirit stones.

26:12.990 --> 26:15.020
- My stones.
- Mine!

26:15.710 --> 26:17.030
- What's wrong?
- My stones.

26:17.260 --> 26:18.100
Stop.

26:20.710 --> 26:21.670
It's all right.

26:21.670 --> 26:22.510
My spirit stones.

26:22.910 --> 26:23.750
Mine.

26:24.150 --> 26:24.990
They're all mine.

26:27.300 --> 26:28.140
Young man,

26:29.190 --> 26:30.910
you should have told me

26:30.910 --> 26:32.020
before you came.

26:32.300 --> 26:33.990
I could have had someone pick you up.

26:34.340 --> 26:35.180
Don't bother.

26:35.870 --> 26:36.780
I've heard

26:36.780 --> 26:37.950
there are many amusements

26:37.950 --> 26:38.790
in your place.

26:39.300 --> 26:40.300
So I came to take a look.

26:40.950 --> 26:42.190
Extraordinary, indeed.

26:43.710 --> 26:44.550
Young man,

26:45.340 --> 26:46.780
you need to pay spirit stones

26:46.990 --> 26:48.300
for pleasures here.

26:48.950 --> 26:50.500
A great many spirit stones.

26:52.670 --> 26:53.740
I heard you're a good gambler.

26:54.740 --> 26:55.630
Would you be interested

26:55.870 --> 26:56.710
in gambling with me?

26:57.340 --> 26:58.180
If you win,

26:58.870 --> 26:59.710
I'll leave now.

27:00.150 --> 27:01.340
But if I win,

27:02.190 --> 27:03.230
let me look around here.

27:03.710 --> 27:04.550
Young man,

27:05.540 --> 27:07.990
haven't you heard about my stories?

27:09.670 --> 27:10.580
In gambling,

27:10.580 --> 27:12.190
I've never lost.

27:13.820 --> 27:15.230
He's challenging Her Ladyship.

27:15.540 --> 27:16.780
How bold of him.

27:17.300 --> 27:18.150
I bet on Her Ladyship.

27:18.150 --> 27:18.990
So do I.

27:19.740 --> 27:21.870
Shoot a jade arrow from 100 steps away

27:22.060 --> 27:24.100
through the leaves of the Money Tree.

27:24.300 --> 27:25.340
One leaf at a time.

27:25.500 --> 27:26.470
Who hits more will win.

27:28.060 --> 27:28.910
The victory depends

27:29.540 --> 27:31.190
on 30 percent luck and 70 percent skill.

27:32.230 --> 27:33.870
Then where should I

27:34.670 --> 27:35.670
use the remaining luck?

27:38.300 --> 27:40.190
Clever man, indeed.

27:40.820 --> 27:42.150
Who rolls higher

27:42.300 --> 27:43.580
will get a chance

27:43.580 --> 27:44.740
to shoot once.

27:45.780 --> 27:46.620
Young man,

27:47.300 --> 27:48.580
let's leave it to luck.

28:13.150 --> 28:14.780
Didn't Simu tell you?

28:15.390 --> 28:17.190
Having senses here

28:17.710 --> 28:18.950
isn't a good thing.

28:27.260 --> 28:29.020
(Boundless Gold)

28:29.260 --> 28:30.100
She hit it.

28:36.870 --> 28:37.710
She's going to win.

28:46.340 --> 28:47.300
I told you.

28:47.300 --> 28:48.340
She'll win.

28:52.860 --> 28:53.710
He's bluffing.

28:53.710 --> 28:54.740
- Yeah.
- Look there.

28:54.740 --> 28:56.060
He rolled a five, so what?

28:56.190 --> 28:57.030
He'll lose anyway.

29:01.260 --> 29:02.340
Twenty-one points.

29:02.990 --> 29:05.540
The best you can do is a tie.

29:05.670 --> 29:06.710
Her Ladyship is the best.

29:11.870 --> 29:13.390
Without the sense of touch,

29:13.870 --> 29:15.060
you can't come up with that.

29:16.580 --> 29:17.420
Twenty-four points.

29:18.430 --> 29:19.270
I win.

29:19.820 --> 29:20.950
I can't believe she lost.

29:27.630 --> 29:28.670
He'll miss.

29:29.500 --> 29:30.380
Look at his posture.

29:30.380 --> 29:31.220
He can't win.

29:31.220 --> 29:32.060
He just can't.

29:32.060 --> 29:32.940
Can he even draw?

29:32.940 --> 29:34.900
(Boundless Gold)

29:36.390 --> 29:37.260
Amazing.

29:37.260 --> 29:38.500
How could he hit like that?

29:38.740 --> 29:39.670
It was just his luck.

29:39.670 --> 29:40.910
You're pretty good.

29:41.670 --> 29:43.500
Then let's play for real

29:47.190 --> 29:48.230
and see what will happen.

30:00.060 --> 30:00.910
Look at Her Ladyship.

30:02.470 --> 30:03.780
I'd like to see

30:03.950 --> 30:05.100
how long you can stay in.

30:12.740 --> 30:13.580
They...

30:13.780 --> 30:14.820
Can't tell who's winning.

30:16.580 --> 30:17.710
It has never happened before.

30:20.300 --> 30:21.140
It seems

30:21.950 --> 30:23.020
we can't have a winner

30:23.020 --> 30:23.860
with the dice.

30:24.820 --> 30:26.260
Even if we compete in shooting,

30:26.260 --> 30:27.710
we'll just have a tie.

30:28.260 --> 30:29.100
Why don't we

30:29.230 --> 30:30.740
make it a bit harder?

30:37.060 --> 30:37.910
Who can hit

30:37.910 --> 30:40.100
one of the falling golden leaves

30:40.430 --> 30:41.390
will be the winner.

30:49.150 --> 30:50.230
Through the ages,

30:50.470 --> 30:52.390
you're the first to have a chance

30:52.540 --> 30:53.630
for a tie with me.

31:01.910 --> 31:02.750
Look.

31:04.340 --> 31:05.180
Look.

31:05.500 --> 31:06.710
- Nice.
- Great.

31:06.710 --> 31:08.020
Her Ladyship is awesome.

31:09.820 --> 31:11.300
She has great archery.

31:11.740 --> 31:12.820
Bravo!

31:13.340 --> 31:14.180
Nice!

31:14.540 --> 31:15.380
Impressive!

31:39.150 --> 31:40.260
Three leaves?

31:40.500 --> 31:41.500
How could he do that?

31:43.340 --> 31:44.190
He's quite a figure.

31:44.340 --> 31:45.180
He won.

31:45.190 --> 31:46.080
My partner won.

31:46.990 --> 31:49.020
Young man, you won.

31:49.950 --> 31:51.870
I'm convinced I lost.

31:52.060 --> 31:53.020
You're too kind.

31:54.710 --> 31:55.780
Never did I expect

31:55.780 --> 31:57.780
this maverick strategy.

31:58.060 --> 31:58.990
I'll keep my promise.

31:59.630 --> 32:00.780
You can enjoy your stroll

32:01.300 --> 32:02.630
all over my place.

32:03.260 --> 32:04.260
What's more,

32:04.430 --> 32:06.020
wherever you want to go,

32:06.020 --> 32:07.020
you can come to me.

32:07.390 --> 32:08.230
I'll take you there.

32:10.540 --> 32:11.380
Thank you.

32:13.020 --> 32:13.860
How come

32:14.390 --> 32:15.430
Her Ladyship lost?

32:15.880 --> 32:16.740
Oh no.

32:16.740 --> 32:18.540
So I would lose everything.

32:18.870 --> 32:21.820
That's thirty years of savings.

32:22.190 --> 32:23.030
When I won,

32:23.780 --> 32:25.190
why would you lose everything?

32:25.710 --> 32:26.950
All the spirits here

32:27.100 --> 32:28.230
bet on Her Ladyship.

32:28.470 --> 32:29.340
Who would know

32:29.340 --> 32:30.390
you could actually win?

32:30.540 --> 32:32.060
Before Her Ladyship competed with you,

32:32.230 --> 32:33.150
she set another game.

32:33.710 --> 32:34.820
Only she bet on you

32:35.340 --> 32:37.020
while we all lost.

32:38.630 --> 32:39.540
Fine. I'll gamble more

32:40.630 --> 32:41.500
and get my money back.

32:42.260 --> 32:43.620
- Let's go.
- What a gambler.

32:45.100 --> 32:46.670
So I was part of her gambling strategy.

33:06.950 --> 33:09.870
Even the best fall sometimes.

33:11.910 --> 33:12.780
Simu,

33:12.780 --> 33:14.580
the mortal you brought back

33:14.820 --> 33:15.710
is truly exceptional.

33:17.190 --> 33:18.630
If you hadn't shown mercy,

33:19.740 --> 33:21.260
how could a mere mortal like him

33:21.260 --> 33:22.230
have won?

33:24.710 --> 33:25.560
I was impressed

33:25.560 --> 33:27.260
by his final move.

33:27.390 --> 33:29.150
I don't want to ruin this fresh feeling.

33:29.870 --> 33:31.580
It's been a few centuries

33:31.580 --> 33:33.470
since I had a worthy opponent last time.

33:33.820 --> 33:35.870
What a mad gambler.

33:45.300 --> 33:46.140
Simu,

33:46.910 --> 33:48.100
he's so interesting.

33:48.500 --> 33:50.060
Let him stay for a few more days.

34:05.100 --> 34:05.940
I should go.

34:15.020 --> 34:15.860
You can bet on big.

35:23.240 --> 35:28.570
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

35:28.900 --> 35:33.150
♪Light encountered shadow♪

35:34.510 --> 35:39.880
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

35:40.180 --> 35:44.780
♪The unbreakable fate♪

35:45.870 --> 35:47.710
♪Suddenly cracked♪

35:59.920 --> 36:05.360
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

36:05.540 --> 36:09.870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

36:11.240 --> 36:16.630
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

36:16.860 --> 36:20.800
♪The unbreakable fate♪

36:22.570 --> 36:24.460
♪Suddenly cracked♪

36:27.120 --> 36:30.280
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

36:30.280 --> 36:32.810
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

36:32.810 --> 36:38.330
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

36:38.330 --> 36:41.570
♪Following fate's guidance♪

36:41.570 --> 36:46.430
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

36:46.770 --> 36:49.790
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

36:49.790 --> 36:52.610
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

36:52.870 --> 36:55.400
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

36:55.400 --> 37:00.820
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

37:00.990 --> 37:04.060
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

37:04.220 --> 37:09.120
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

37:09.330 --> 37:12.800
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
